OL,3,CPaying the price - MSPs debate
OL,4,CScottish bank closures
OL,6,FA South Scotland MSP secured a debate
OL,7,Fat Holyrood to discuss a spate of bank
OL,8,Fbranch closures affecting towns in the
OL,9,Fregion.
OL,11,FCraig Hoy, a Conservative MSP, told
OL,12,Fthe Scottish Parliament on Thursday:
OL,13,F"Banks are commercial entities, they
OL,14,Fare free to make their own commercial
OL,15,Fdecisions. I recognise that.
OL,17,F"But they also have a duty to their
OL,18,Fcustomers, particularly older
OL,19,Fcustomers and small businesses, who
OL,20,Foften live and operate in small towns
OL,21,Fand in rural areas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
