OL,3,CPaying the price - MSPs debate
OL,4,CScottish bank closures
OL,6,F"I have heard far too often from
OL,7,Fconstituents who feel that high street
OL,8,Fbanks have abandoned them."
OL,10,FThe debate followed a series of bank
OL,11,Fclosures affecting towns in Dumfries
OL,12,Fand Galloway and the Borders this
OL,13,Fyear, with the Bank of Scotland having
OL,14,Falready closed branches in Langholm
OL,15,Fand Newton Stewart.
OL,17,FThe last remaining bank in Moffat is
OL,18,Fset to close in November, while Castle
OL,19,FDouglas is set to lose its branch in
OL,20,FJanuary 2026, and Annan's is due to be
OL,21,Fshuttered in March.
