OL,6,FOn the Moffat closure, Mr Hoy said:
OL,7,F"This leaves this vibrant tourist and
OL,8,Fretirement town without a bank, easily
OL,9,Faccessible high street ATM, or banking
OL,10,Fhub."
OL,12,FA campaigner against the closures from
OL,13,FMoffat, Evelyn Atkins, attended the
OL,14,FScottish Parliament to hear the debate.
OL,16,FThe cash access and ATM network has
OL,17,Fconfirmed that a hub in Annan is among
OL,18,F22 it will open to help plug the gaps
OL,19,Fleft by branch closures.
