OL,4,CScottish bank closures
OL,6,FSNP MSP for Moray, and Minister for
OL,7,FBusiness Richard Lochhead said: "I
OL,8,Fshare the concerns shared by many
OL,9,Fmembers. While the regulation of
OL,10,Fnational services is a reserved
OL,11,Fmatter, the Scottish Government has
OL,12,Fbeen proactive in our engagements with
OL,13,Fthe sector and regulator to advocate
OL,14,Ffor Scotland's interests.
OL,16,F"The expansion of banking hubs across
OL,17,FScotland has been positively received
OL,18,Fby those communities which have
OL,19,Fbenefitted."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
