OL,6,F"Two new funds have been launched to
OL,7,Fsupport digital inclusion work in
OL,8,FScotland. It's important that we take
OL,9,Fmeasures to ensure people are not left
OL,10,Fbehind and are able to access banking
OL,11,Fservices through digital means."
OL,13,FA Bank of Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"The way people are banking has
OL,15,Fchanged, as many customers are
OL,16,Fmanaging their money through our app.
OL,17,FWe're providing more choice than ever
OL,18,Fbefore, bringing together the best in
OL,19,Fdigital convenience with our people.
